WEBVTT

0
00:00:00.439 --> 00:00:03.339
Communication and updates are recorded directly on the task.

1
00:00:04.230 --> 00:00:07.550
Use Work Notes to record internal updates as work progresses.

2
00:00:08.590 --> 00:00:10.850
These updates are not visible to the requester.

3
00:00:15.760 --> 00:00:17.200
If more information is needed,

4
00:00:17.440 --> 00:00:21.149
an Additional Comment can be added to obtain clarification from the requester.

5
00:00:29.610 --> 00:00:30.690
When waiting for a response,

6
00:00:30.770 --> 00:00:32.709
the task can be placed in a Pending state.

7
00:00:40.689 --> 00:00:43.970
The Comment is automatically posted to the Requested Item record,

8
00:00:44.209 --> 00:00:47.130
where it is visible to the requester and triggers a notification.

9
00:00:48.869 --> 00:00:50.200
When the requester responds,

10
00:00:50.459 --> 00:00:52.110
as the Assigned To user,

11
00:00:52.360 --> 00:00:54.279
you'll be notified that a comment has been added.

12
00:00:56.790 --> 00:00:58.560
Once the required information is received,

13
00:00:58.639 --> 00:01:01.319
the task can be returned to the Work in Progress state.
